gw.bizrules.pcf

Interface BizRulesPageNavigationSupport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBizRulesPageNavigationSupport

    public interface BizRulesPageNavigationSupport
    An abstraction around UI of Business Rules. The shared components use it to navigate to a given page or open a specific popup which are only implemented on the application side.
